English:
//HearSay auto-transcript begins// 
 
VOICE 1 
You can do it from this terminal?

I think so, yes. 
 
VOICE 1

VOICE 1

VOICE 2 
That's the plan. 
 
VOICE 1 
Great. Do it. What was that? 
 
VOICE 2 
Let's see... what is this? W-R-D-N? 
 
VOICE 1 
You didn't hear that? 
 
VOICE 2 
No. There's a... this doesn't make any sense. There's a... process running here that shouldn't be able to-- 
 
VOICE 1

VOICE 2 
I'm working on it! 
 
VOICE 1 
What is that?! Hello? Is there someone there?  
 
VOICE 3 
Destination reached. 
 
VOICE 4 
Holding. 
 
VOICE 1 
My god... we didn't think anyone was... we're from the World Health Organization. Are you-- 
 
VOICE 4 
Stack updated. 
 
VOICE 3 
Engaging. 
 
VOICE 1 
Hey whoa! What are you doing-- 
 
//HearSay auto-transcript ends//
